# Projocalypse package manager (locked)

## pnpm only

- **pnpm only** — never `npm install`, `npm ci`, `yarn`, or commit `package-lock.json` / `yarn.lock`.
- Root `packageManager` field pins pnpm; use `pnpm add`, `pnpm install`, `pnpm exec`.
- Lockfile: **`pnpm-lock.yaml`** at repo root.

## Commands

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Install deps | `pnpm install` |
| Dev server | `pnpm dev` (port **5173**, `strictPort`) |
| Check / free dev port | `pnpm dev:port:check`, `pnpm dev:port:free` |
| Production build | `pnpm build` |
| Lint | `pnpm lint` |
| Preview build | `pnpm preview` |
| Add dependency | `pnpm add <pkg>` |
| Add dev dependency | `pnpm add -D <pkg>` |

## When editing

- After changing `package.json`, run `pnpm install` and commit `pnpm-lock.yaml` with the change.
- Agents and docs use `pnpm` / `pnpm run <script>` — not `npm run`.

Related: **`projocalypse-stack.mdc`**, **`projocalypse-feature-ship.mdc`**, **`projocalypse-dev-server.mdc`**.
